simgui (0.5.19-1) unstable; urgency=high

  * Blank card safety: skip VERIFY ADM1 on unpersonalised cards.
    Blank cards have no ADM1 set, so VERIFY consumes retry attempts uselessly.
    authenticate() now detects blank cards (empty _original_card_data or
